metadata.name: No Reddit - 500Milly
metadata.description:
Hit single "No Reddit" by 500 Milly

Formerly the Artist known as G.E.M.S in Web2.  This is the Genesis Music NFT drop from the long time recording artist 500Milly paired with incredibly high quality animated 3D art created by Elian Jaku, creator of the Holoheadz project on the Polygon Network.

The content of this song was inspired by events and conversations that happened /occurred during Q4 of 2022 live in Twitter Spaces

Follow on twitter: @five00million & @elianjaku

Worldwide streaming release date is 12/31/2022 at 11:59 pm Only this NFT will feature the high resolution animated 3D art.

The Music and Art are the Utility!  Much Love to the NFT and Crypto Community
